elements.old_text:
On this 5-night, 6-day French vacation from Amazing Value 
Vacations, youll create your own itinerary, free to explore the 
french countryside or its beautiful coasts. After spending one 
night at the 4-star LuxHotel in Nice, youll choose from any 
of the bed and breakfasts listed on B&B France.
